</header>

<main>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">💧 Water &amp; Drink Intake Reminder</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Drink more water.<br><span>Feel the difference.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Hydrate Daily is the calm, effortless water tracker your body deserves — no dashboards, no stress, no subscriptions. Free forever.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <!-- Update href to App Store URL once the app is live -->
      <a href="#" class="btn-store">
